    ('3076','Defense','Colin Brooks','Special Assistant, Office of the Under Secretary of Defense (Policy)',NULL,NULL,'157253','2018-07-09 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,13,'colin-brooks',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'defense',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'The son of a lawyer and Protestant pastor, Brooks decided to join the Army when he was in high school in Cleveland. ‚ÄúI‚Äôve always liked being a part of something that‚Äôs bigger than me,‚Äù he said.

