    ('2964','State','Caroline Casagrande','Deputy Assistant Secretary, Bureau of Education and Cultural Affairs',NULL,NULL,'134789','2018-09-02 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,12,'caroline-casagrande',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'state',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Previously, Ms. Casagrande served as the Special Advisor to ECA Assistant Secretary Marie Royce, providing senior-level advice on the formulation of public diplomacy programming to support the National Security Strategy. She has led new initiatives on a broad range of educational and cultural exchange programming to support global women‚Äôs economic empowerment, religious freedom, and countering state-sponsored disinformation.

