    ('3138','Federal Trade Commission','Erie K. Meyer','Technology Advisor, Office of the Chairman',NULL,NULL,'143774','2018-06-11 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,50,'erie-k-meyer',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'federal-trade-commission',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Erie Meyer, a co-founder of the U.S. Digital Service, is returning to the federal government.

