    ('2916','Interior','Mark Antonio Cruz','Deputy Assistant Secretary, Policy and Economic Development, Indian Affairs',NULL,NULL,'162000','2018-09-24 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,33,'mark-antonio-cruz',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'interior',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Mark Cruz, an enrolled member of the Klamath Tribes in Oregon, is the Deputy Assistant Secretary‚ÄìIndian Affairs for Policy and Economic Development (DAS-PED).  He was appointed to that post by Assistant Secretary‚ÄìIndian Affairs Tara Karuk Mac Lean Sweeney on September 24, 2018.  The DAS-PED oversees the Office of Indian Energy and Economic Development (IEED) and the Office of Self-Governance (OSG).

